ply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Tormax/Vindi/NTOV/Luclin Tactics. Please read :</span><hr size=1> Something that's really making me hate coming to the safehouse is the huge number of posts that say 'XXX tactics?&quot; followed by 14 people who think they are witty when they say 'hit autoattack'<br>
<br>
Yeah I know, I can just skip these posts, and that's fine, but I'd rather offer a positive and creative solution.  So without further ado, to keep all the 'witty' people in check and also keep people from asking 'how do i kill XXX' instead of specific questions, is a basic rundown of what EVERY mob in velious and above requires.<br>
<br>
1) You must attack it.  This is done by melee.<br>
2) Nuke it, this is done by nukers.<br>
3) heal everyone.  This is done by healers.<br>
4) Debuff it.  This includes MR debuff, Disease rebuff, Fire debuff, Cripple, Slow (if it works on this mob), AC Debuff.<br>
5) Buff your group suffeciently before attacking.  Hp, AC, Resists, +Atk, Dmg Shields for tanks, and the like.<br>
<br>
Now, when asking how to kill a mob, please ask these specific questions.<br>
<br>
1) What resists, if any, are needed?<br>
2) What spells is this mob immune to? (Slows, etc)<br>
3) does this mob dispell AoE, or himself?<br>
4) What is this monster unusually resistant to?<br>
5) What is this monster unusually weak to?<br>
6) How much melee damage does this mob put out?<br>
7) Does he require a main tank strategy, or a zergling all out damage rush?<br>
<br>
That should clear up one of the most bitter, and silly, problems that the safehouse is currently undergoing.  I think every time a post like this appears it nearly approaches a level of name calling, and I'm positive that if the rules didnt forbid it, it would (monkly-business.com anybody?)<br>
<br>
But its simple.  If someone wants a spoiler, either give it to them, or dont.  But relax <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->     Take it easy?  Enjoy the board <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
<br>
Sorry if this sounds like i'm trying to run the safehouse, and if its bad or uppity, feel free to just delete it mods.  But I cant imagine you arent tired of it as well.<br>
